ti_sci_msg_resp_query_clock_freq Struct Reference

#include <pmhal_ti_sci.h>

Detailed Description

struct ti_sci_msg_resp_query_clock_freq - Response to a clock frequency query : Generic Header : Frequency that is the best match in Hz.

Response to request type TI_SCI_MSG_QUERY_CLOCK_FREQ. NOTE: if the request cannot be satisfied, the message will be of type NACK.
